high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the sink.
Pick the spoon up from the left side of the sink.
Turn around and stand in front of the stove.
Put the spoon in the drawer to the left of the stove and shut the drawer.
Go stand in front of the white table in front of the spoon.
Pick the spoon up from the white table.
Turn around and stand in front of the sink.
Open the drawer to the left and put the spoon in and shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees and turn to the right 90 degrees when you reach the sink.
Pick up the spoon next to the sink.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk to the counter.
Open the drawer and put the spoon inside, closing the drawer after.
Walk to the table located in the corner of the room.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk back towards the drawer from step 4.
Open the drawer and put the spoon inside, closing the drawer after.
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons from the kitchen into a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the spoon at the sink.
Turn around to face the coffee maker, then turn left.
Put the spoon in the left most drawer.
Go forward then turn right, then turn left to approach the table.
Pick up the spoon on the table, next to the egg.
Turn around and return to the drawer with the spoon in it.
Place the spoon in the drawer, next to the other stone.
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around until you get to the sink, then turn to your right and face it
Pick up a spoon off of the kitchen counter
Turn around and face the other way, then turn to your left
Open the kitchen drawer, place the spoon in it and then close it.
Turn left, then right towards the wall, then face left at the white table
Pick a spoon up off of the white table
Go back to where you were before at the drawer
Open the kitchen drawer, place the other spoon in it and then close it.
anns.task_desc: Place 2 spoons in the kitchen drawer
